00:42:03.847 --> 00:42:06.507
by giving them some experiences

1031
00:42:06.507 --> 00:42:09.247
of evaluating how important this is.

1032
00:42:09.247 --> 00:42:10.546
You know, buying a little time

1033
00:42:10.546 --> 00:42:12.667
