00:42:42.487 --> 00:42:45.447
when Michael Jackson died, I was

1050
00:42:45.447 --> 00:42:47.847
thinking of what I have in the book

1051
00:42:47.847 --> 00:42:49.267
called the Money Life Drain.

1052
00:42:49.267 --> 00:42:52.767
