1057
00:43:05.247 --> 00:43:06.467
They talked about the fact,

1058
00:43:06.467 --> 00:43:11.407
let's just remove the whole idea of drugs, okay.

1059
00:43:11.407 --> 00:43:14.507
He had behaviors with money for a long time

1060
00:43:14.507 --> 00:43:16.007
that had been in the news,

1061
00:43:16.007 --> 00:43:18.147
and people talked about his compulsive shopping,

1062
00:43:18.147 --> 00:43:19.667
and all of his debt.

