1083
00:44:19.838 --> 00:44:22.118
But he was caught in the Money Life Drain,

1084
00:44:22.118 --> 00:44:24.178
and he needed to go on that tour

1085
00:44:24.178 --> 00:44:26.118
to satisfy his creditors and keep from

1086
00:44:26.118 --> 00:44:27.658
losing some of his property.

1087
00:44:27.658 --> 00:44:32.038
And, so I really feel that that really did lead--

1088
00:44:32.038 --> 00:44:35.058
[Regina] That makes sense.

1089
00:44:35.058 --> 00:44:36.758
<v ->You add the other addictions, and I know</v>

