00:44:36.758 --> 00:44:39.398
it's a bigger, more complex story than that,

1091
00:44:39.398 --> 00:44:40.128
but--

1092
00:44:40.128 --> 00:44:41.328
[Regina] But if you're about to lose

1093
00:44:41.328 --> 00:44:42.768
your dream because you've overspent.

1094
00:44:42.768 --> 00:44:46.008
And he had a big dream, and overspent in a big way.

1095
00:44:46.008 --> 00:44:47.728
Of course, he's gotta be suffering

1096
00:44:47.728 --> 00:44:49.868
from severe anxiety and lack of sleep.

1097
00:44:49.868 --> 00:44:51.728
And it makes sense that he would be

1098
00:44:51.728 --> 00:44:54.348
